People watch a sound and light show at the Grand Place in Brussels, Belgium, July 29, 2020. A sound and light show was held at the Grand Place of Brussels to highlight Belgium's missing events in this summer due to the COVID-19 pandemic. (Xinhua/Zheng Huansong)  

